Summary: pscp suffers an assertion failure when a remote file changes size
Class: bug
Difficulty: tricky
Priority: high
Present-in: 0.60 2007-05-04 r7503
Content-type: text/plain

When copying a file from a remote system whose size changes during a copy
(for instance, an active log file), pscp suffers an assertion failure:

  Assertion failed: actuallen <= len, file ..\pscp.c, line 1523

